Title: Do You See Me?
Writer: Giulia Calenda (story), Paola Cortellesi (story), Furio Andreotti (story), Ivan Cotroneo (story), Riccardo Milani (story), Giulia Calenda (screenplay), Paola Cortellesi (screenplay), Furio Andreotti (screenplay), Riccardo Milani (screenplay)
Actors: Paola Cortellesi, Raoul Bova, Corrado Fortuna, Ennio Fantastichini
Plot: Serena Bruno returns to Italy to be an architect and help people but she will struggle to convince her fellow co-workers that they have to be more open minded.
